(2, 'Discounted First Class Tickets Lufthansa, Cheap Business Class Flights , last minute flights LUfthansa', 'Cheap Business class flight with Lufthansa, discounted business class tickets, first class flight Lufthansa', 'Lufthansa', 'Business-Flights-First-Class-Lufthansa', 'Cheap First Class Tickets & Discounted Business Class Fare on Lufthansa ', '&#160;Cheap Business &amp; First Class Flights on Lufthansa. Best Business Class Deals. Save Thousands on Last Minute Business Class Tickets. Affordable Price for Business Class Seats. Call Us Now to Book &amp; Save up to 70%\n', '<h4><strong>FlyFirst offers cheap Business Class flights on Lufthansa, we specialize on last minute business class tickets, FlyFirst provides discounted First Class fares on Lufthansa. Best Business Class Deals. Save Thousands on Business and First Class Tickets. Discount First &amp; Business Class Airline Tickets. First Class &amp; Business Class Travel Deals.</strong></h4>\n\n    <p><span style="color:#A9A9A9;"><span style="font-size:16px;">With FlyFirst.com and Lufthansa, you&#39;ll save as much as 70 percent on luxury airfare and enjoy all of Lufthansa&#39;s extensive and much-lauded services.</span></span></p>\n\n    <h2>About Lufthansa</h2>\n\n    <p>As the fourth largest air carrier in the world, Lufthansa is a titan in the airline industry. The privately owned airline maintains the world&#39;s largest aircraft fleet, operates its hub at Frankfurt Airport and houses its headquarters in Cologne, Germany. With more than 116,000 employees, Lufthansa flies to 197 international destinations. The company holds 14 subsidiaries, including Austrian Airlines, Swiss European Air Lines and Tyrolean Airways, offering flexibility and choice for passengers.<br />\n    <br />\n    Lufthansa&#39;s services are legendary. Airline reviewer SkyTrax recently evaluated Lufthansa&#39;s <strong>first class services</strong> and awarded the company with the top five-star designation. In the ratings, SkyTrax noted Lufthansa&#39;s comfortable seats that recline to a fully flat position, its variety of in-flight entertainment and its outstanding on-board staff service.</p>\n\n    <h2>First Class At The Airport</h2>\n\n    <p>As if a five-star rating isn&#39;t enough, Lufthansa recently upgraded its already-extravagant first and business class services. The company opened five new premium lounges in its Frankfurt First Class Terminal devoted entirely to its top-tier passengers. Here, passengers enjoy high-end toiletries, daybeds in quiet rooms, a cigar lounge, hot and cold meals and an extensive wine list. Passengers are delivered directly to their aircraft in sumptuous limousines after passing through special customs and security queues.&#160;<br />\n    <br />\n    In addition to the special first class terminal, Lufthansa operates several first class lounges in the Frankfurt Airport, as well as in airports in <strong>Munich, Dusseldorf, New York, Geneva and Zurich</strong>.</p>\n\n    <h2>First Class In The Air at Discounted Price</h2>\n\n    <p>I<span style="line-height: 1.6em;">n first class, passengers flying out of Germany and other European cities enjoy exclusive caviar service, a &quot;Culinary Delights&quot; menu that changes bi-monthly, appetizers with a wide range of canap&eacute;s and table service featuring top-of-the-line linens and glassware.</span></p>\n\n    <h2>Business Class Flights Very Cheap</h2>\n\n    <p>In business class, passengers boarding flights in Europe delight in fresh meals served on quality china. On flights lasting more than 76 minutes, travelers enjoy a delectable dessert with choices of fresh fruit, sweet treats or ice cream. Seats on newer aircraft lie completely flat for restful sleeping and contain expanded seat-back entertainment screens. On long-haul flights, passengers can adjust seat angles with their own smart phones and extend the seat to a full six and-a-half feet flat bed.</p>\n\n    <h2>Lufthansa and FlyFirst.com</h2>\n\n    <p>Whether you choose to travel in Lufthansa&#39;s <strong>first or business class options</strong>, FlyFirst.com ensures that you enjoy all of the lavish amenities and services at a fraction of the regular rates. Together, Lufthansa and FlyFirst.com offer you tremendous value on <strong>first class flights and business class seats</strong>.</p>\n', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
