(15, 'First Class Airfares, Business Class Airfares, Cheap Last Minute First Class Airline Cheap', 'First class airfares, business class airfares, class airfares cheap business', 'All Nippon Airline', 'Business-Class-Cheap-Discount-All-Nippon-Airline', 'Last Minute First Class Tickets, Discounted Business Class Flights on All Nippon Airline', 'FlyFirst offers cheap Business Class flights to Asia, we specialize on last minute business class tickets, FlyFirst provides discounted First Class fares to Asia. Best Business Class Deals. Save Thousands on Business and First Class Tickets. Discount First &amp; Business Class Airline Tickets. First Class &amp; Business Class Travel Deals.\n', '<p><strong>Cheap Business &amp; First Class Flights to Asia. Best Business Class Deals. Save Thousands on Last Minute Business Class Tickets. Affordable Price for Business Class Seats. Call Us Now to Book &amp; Save up to 70%</strong></p>\n\n    <h2>About All Nippon Airlines</h2>\n\n    <p>With more than 14,000 employees, Tokyo-based All Nippon Airlines (ANA) serves 81 domestic and international cities with a fleet of 226 aircraft. The largest airline in Japan, ANA provided transport for more than 47 million passengers in 2012. In 2013, the airline was awarded SkyTrax&#39; top five-star rating for its broad range of services and amenities. FlightStats ranked the airline No. 1 for its on-time performance, and<em>Air Transport World</em>&#160;recognized the air carrier with the &quot;2012 Airline of the Year Award.&quot;</p>\n\n    <h2>ANA At The Airport</h2>\n\n    <p>All Nippon operates ANA Lounges at various Japanese and international airports. First and business class passengers can dine on light meals, refresh in a shower suite or a massage chair, relax in supple arm chairs or catch up on work at Internet connection sites.</p>\n\n    <h2>First Class</h2>\n\n    <p>First class seats offer exclusive privacy in individual shell or cubicle configurations. Both offer over-sized seats that