(23, 'Cheap First Class Tickets, Discount Business Class Fare, Last Minute First Class', 'Last Minute Business Class Fare, First Class Tickets, Cheap Business Class', 'Virgin Atlantic', 'First-Class-Cheap-Virgin-Atlantic', 'Cheap Business & Discounted First Class with Virgin Atlantic', 'FlyFirst offers cheap Business Class flights On Virgin Atlantic, we specialize on last minute business class tickets, FlyFirst provides discounted First Class fares to Europe. Best Business Class Deals. Save Thousands on Business and First Class Tickets. Discount First &amp; Business Class Airline Tickets. First Class &amp; Business Class Travel Deals\r\n', '<p><strong>Cheap Business &amp; First Class Flights Virgin Atlantic. Best Business Class Deals. Save Thousands on Last Minute Business Class Tickets. Affordable Price for Business Class Seats. Call Us Now to Book &amp; Save up to 70%</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contemporary interiors and purple-hued lighting are the hallmarks of Virgin Atlantic&#39;s cabins, but the airline offers so much more for its <strong>premium passengers</strong>. Relish Virgin Atlantic&#39;s luxury while saving thousands of dollars with FlyFirst.com&#39;s <strong>discount first class fares and business class seats</strong>. You&#39;ll save as much as 70 percent on published fares and reap all of the sumptuous full-price services.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>About Virgin Atlantic</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Based near England&#39;s Gatwick Airport, Virgin Atlantic was established in 1984 to serve passengers traveling between England and New York. Today, Virgin Atlantic transports more than 5.3 million passengers each year to 34 destinations in North America, Europe, the Middle East, Australia, the Caribbean and Africa. In 2013, the company launched a short-haul service within the United Kingdom named Little Red. Committed to environmental concerns, Virgin Atlantic was the first commercial airline in the world to operate a flight using a biofuel blend, and the air carrier continues to work on creating a low-carbon aviation fuel. Often lauded for its service, Virgin Atlantic was named by Conde Nast&nbsp;<em>Traveller</em>as the best long-haul leisure airline in 2011.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Virgin Atlantic At The Airport</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Chic, contemporary and overflowing with posh amenities, Virgin Atlantic&#39;s airport lounges receive abundant attention from industry leaders, travelers and the press corps. The airline&#39;s newest airport clubhouses at New York&#39;s JFK and Newark airports showcase the airline&#39;s iconic style. At JFK, mingle with other &quot;Upper Class&quot; passengers at the swanky cocktail bar, relax in designer lounge chairs or take care of last-minute work issues at computer workstations. Many of Virgin&#39;s airport lounges also offer spa and salon services such as those found at its flagship clubhouse in Heathrow Airport. There, Upper Class passengers relish a water wall cascading into a relaxing pool, a multi-screen entertainment area, a brasserie, a deli and a library.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Upper Class</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>For <strong>business class passengers</strong>, Virgin offers its Upper Class program featuring chauffeur transfer services to and from the airport, private security lines, supple leather seats that all directly access the aisle and on-board lounges. The touch of a button converts the comfortable Upper Class seat into an extra-wide flat bed that stretches six-and-a-half feet. Passengers enjoy ample work space and amenities that include power ports, a spacious table and laptop storage space. Entertainment systems with plenty of movies, television shows and games help travelers pass the time, and mood lighting creates a restful, serene on-board ambiance.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Virgin Atlantic and FlyFirst.com</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>FlyFirst.com frequently works with Virgin Atlantic to offer the very best deals on its Upper Class cabins. With FlyFirst.com, you&#39;ll save bundles of money on <strong>first class fares</strong> and <strong>business class seats</strong> aboard premium airlines like Virgin Atlantic so that you can enjoy an affordable, <strong>luxury travel experience</strong>.</p>\r\n', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-04-22 18:26:21');
